# SIMON-TECH-BOT - Node.js WhatsApp Bot

## Get started

Install dependencies with npm
```
npm install
```

Generate session ID
```
npm run session
```

Create .env file from .env.example
```
cp .env.example .env
```

Start the bot
```
npm start
```

Or in development mode:
```
npm run dev
```

## Features

- 200+ Commands
- AI System
- Game System
- Economy System
- Media Tools
- Security System
- Group Management
- And Much More!

